name: Upgrade Your Chains!
description:
All VLING necklaces come on 18 inch curb chain as a default.

If you'd prefer a longer length, we offer a thicker curb chain, or ball chain in 20, 24 and 28 inch lengths.

If you'd like a custom length, please use the contact form to message us and we'll be happy to meet your needs.

Currently only silver is available for the upgrades.

name: Necklace and Earring Sizing
description:

Please email us and specify if you'd like them in the smaller size.

Earrings are  around 1.5 inches by 1.5 inches.
